\{E_k\}
\displaystyle \bigg \vert \bigcup_k E_k \bigg \vert = \sum_k \vert E_k \vert
E_k
k \in \mathbb N
\varepsilon > 0
F_k \subseteq E_k
\vert E_k - F_k \vert < \varepsilon2^{-k}
\vert E_k \vert \leq \vert F_k \vert + \varepsilon 2^{-k}
E = \bigcup E_k
\vert E \vert \leq \sum \vert E_k \vert
\vert E_k \vert \leq \vert F_k \vert + \varepsilon 2^{-k}
